  "title": "Retail Supervisor #82134",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Fine Jewellery Manufacturer & Retailer</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Retail Supervisor</strong></li><li>Working Location: Central</li><li>Working Hours: 5-day work week on a rotating roster, including weekends, from Monday to Sunday, 11:00am to 7:00pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + Commission + Performance Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver personalised, high-quality service to clients.</li><li>Drive sales and support the team in achieving targets.</li><li>Build and maintain strong relationships with VIP clients.</li><li>Manage CRM records and ensure excellent after-sales service.</li><li>Lead by example and contribute to a positive team culture.</li><li>Support stock control, replenishment, and inventory accuracy.</li><li>Perform other duties assigned by management.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>At least 5 years of experience in luxury retail, preferably jewellery or high-end products.</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Passion for luxury, design, and client service.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#82134 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
